A9 - File Systems
=====================

Overview
==========
Lab number 9 of **AWS Cloud Quest: Cloud Practitioner** is **File System in the Cloud using Amazon EFS**

1.In the city interface

. Select ASSIGNMENTS
. Select ROUTE AND GO


.. image:: pictures/route_and_go1.png
   :align: center
   :width: 700px

2.In the city interface

. Select the ! icon


.. image:: pictures/route_and_go2.png
   :align: center
   :width: 700px

3.In the **File System in the Cloud** interface

. View **Rewards**
. Select **NEXT**


.. image:: pictures/route_and_go3.png
   :align: center
   :width: 700px

4.In the **File Systems in the Cloud** interface

. See **Solution Annotations**
. **Select ACCEPT**


.. image:: pictures/route_and_go4.png
   :align: center
   :width: 700px


5.In the **File Systems in the Cloud** interface

Select **GO TO SOLUTION CENTER** to prepare the next steps


.. image:: pictures/route_and_go5.png
   :align: center
   :width: 700px


